List 98-140
Titles from Lebanon

1-	LCN: 98963168
 
 Isma'il, 'Adil. Azmat al-fikr al-Lubnani fi kitabat 
tarikh Lubnan wa-fi tawthiqih : asrar fi masirat nashr 
al-watha'iq al-diblumasiyah wa-al-fadliyah 
al-muta'alliqah bi-tarikh Lubnan wa-buldan al-Sharq 
al-Adna min al-qarn al-sabi' 'ashar hatta yawmina / 
'Adil Isma'il ; al-muqaddimah bi-qalam Nasri Salhab ; 
al-khatimah bi-qalam Munir Isma'il. al-Tab'ah 1. Bayrut 
: Dar al-Nashr lil-Siyasah wa-al-Tarikh, 1997. $7.00 
(U.S.). 144 p. : ill. ; 22 cm. Includes bibliographical 
references and index. On the crisis of intellectual 
life in Lebanon; history. 
 
 
