5-	LCN: 98963170
 
 Shirazi, Ibrahim ibn 'Ali. [Nukat al-masa'il ] Kitab 
al-Nukat al-masa'il : al-mahdhuf minhu 'Uun al-dala'il 
: al-'ibadat / ta'lif Abi Ishaq Ibrahim ibn 'Ali 
al-Shirazi ; dirasat wa-tahqiq Yasin ibn Nasir 
al-Khatib. al-Tab'ah 1. Bayrut : 'Alam al-Kutub, 1998. 
$9.00 (U.S.). 432 p. : ill. ; 24 cm. Includes 
bibliographical references and indexes. A classic work 
on Islamic doctrines; Islamic law, referring to point 
of controversy between Hanafi and Shafiites, edited by 
a modern scholar. 
 
 
